      • RoutingResolveResult

        public RoutingResolveResult(boolean succeeded,
                            Route route,
                            io.ktor.util.ValuesMap values,
                            double quality)

        Represents a result of routing resolution

        参数:
        succeeded - indicates if resolution succeeded
        route - specifies a routing node for successful resolution, or nearest one for failed
        values - holds all captured values from selectors
        quality - represents quality value for resolution result
